children.value: Software Developer with experience in development and testing of 2G, Single RAN applications
Expertise in OAM software management application (C, C++ and Google Test framework).

Project SRAN -OAM system[LNT-Client SAMSUNG]
Description OAM system takes care of loading and maintaining all applications running in Network entity (BSC/RNC/MBS).
Software Management [SWM] module which is a part of OAM, which takes care of Installation, Up gradation, Resetting, Rebooting, Monitoring, Activating of Firmware & Softwareâ€™s and Provides Inventory Information of the system.
Roles and Responsibilities
  • Developer, Tester
  • Designing of High Level & Detail Level Document for SWM module.
  • Coding for SWM Module.
  • Unit testing using Google Test for SWM.
  • Test Case preparation and Block test using CLI, WEBEMT & EMS tool.
  • Maintenance and Enhancement of the SWM module.
  • Automating the BT test cases using python and XML scripts
Tools & Technology C,c++,sql,Python
Achievements Awarded start of the month award for fixing critical bugs and automating the BT cases
Instrumental in resolving NE loading issues, NE pkg update and supporting other teams to make setup fully functional.

Project 2G-GSM-OAM system[LNT -client SAMSUNG]
Description Involved in development, testing and maintaining of the GSM specific OAM features. I was involved in the software management module (SWM) of the OAM. SWM takes care of the loading, monitoring, rebooting and other software related activities.
Updated the FW through UBOOT method when system is down to make it up.
Roles and Responsibilities
  • Developer, Tester
  • Coding for SWM Module.
  • Unit testing using Google Test for SWM.
  • Manual Block testing using CLI, WEBEMT & EMS tool.
  • Maintenance and Enhancement of the SWM module.
  • Automating the BT test cases using python and XML scripts
Tools & Technology C,C++,python,XML,clearcase,svn
Achievements Managed to communicate and work with Korean client in a short span of time.
Got appreciation from Manager for automating the BT cases,resolving NE loading issues and also for supporting call, System Integration, System Verification teams regarding NE setup and NE loading issues.
